commentAnnotations.text: The name and numbering of the protocol is based on a new numbering system followed by the Sponsor.
Any patient withdrawing from the study after Week 5 and prior to the Week 23 visit will be considered a non-responder.
Footnote I: Qualifying patients at participating sites may have study drug dosed at home during certain visits in Part B.
Footnote c: Revaccination with booster doses should be given according to regional guidelines for patients with persistent complement deficiency.
